steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' link on the Folder page
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Enter a library name in 'Name' input field under 'Library'
Enter a 'main' value in the 'Default version' input field
Open a 'Source Code Management' dropdown menu
Enter 'https://github.com/darinpope/github-api-global-lib.git' value in 'Library Path' input field
Validate 'currentDefaultVersion' label
